videos.description: Brandon Silvers completes pass to Damion Willis for a nine-yard touchdown pass.
videos.headline: Troy QB Silvers connects with Willis for game's first score

videos.description: Tyler Rogers connects with Jaleel Scott for a 23-yard pass bringing Aggies to the Troy 26-yard line.
videos.headline: New Mexico State's Scott make contested grab; puts Aggies just outside red zone

videos.description: Brandon Silvers hits Jamarius Henderson for a 20-yard pass bringing Troy near midfield.
videos.headline: Troy RB Henderson turns short pass into big gain

videos.description: Jordan Chunn takes the handoff and goes up the middle for a three-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Troy RB Chunn powers in for rushing TD

videos.description: Josh Anderson runs over defender during his 16-yard run.
videos.headline: Troy RB Anderson trucks over defender

videos.description: Jamarius Henderson sprints forward 21 yards and to the New Mexico State three-yard line.
videos.headline: Troy RB Henderson's 21-yard dash puts them in red zone

videos.description: Jamarius Henderson takes the handoff up the middle for a three-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Troy's Henderson pushes up middle for the TD

videos.description: New Mexico State QB Tyler Rogers jumps up high and grabs the ball for the touchdown.
videos.headline: New Mexico State WR Scott wins jump ball for the TD

videos.description: Shon Spralling takes the snap 32 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Troy's Spralling breaks free for 32-yard TD

videos.description: Larry Rose III runs for 32 yards and moves New Mexico State inside the red zone.
videos.headline: New Mexico State's Rose III's 32 yard carry put them in red zone.

videos.description: Tyler Rogers completes pass to Izaiah Lottie for nine yards and a touchdown.
videos.headline: New Mexico State WR Lottie's 2nd TD cuts into lead

videos.description: Tyler Rogers completes pass to Jaleel Scott for the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: New Mexico State's two-point conversion brings Troy within  three
